T/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/300185358/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Catania</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;WorkShop su Site Editor e temi a blocchi WordPress Meetup Catania&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/meetup-wordpress-catania/events/300164414\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Terni</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 18 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;WordPress e Associazionismo&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-terni/events/300292842\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Zagarolo</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 19 apr, ore 18:00, &#8220;WordPress Women Empower&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/zagarolo-wordpress-meetup/events/300053477\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vicenza</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 23 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;La nostra cassetta degli attrezzi: plugin, addon, app e tool online preferiti.&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-meetup-vicenza/events/300373978\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cagliari</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 23 apr, ore 19:00, &#8220;Oltre i confini: Guida alle Traduzioni su WordPress ed iniziamo a contribuire&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/cagliari-wordpress-meetup/events/300315848\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-dark-blueberry-color has-blueberry-3-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color